debrief.itemText: Please answer the following questions about your experience. Click and drag the red scrollbar to move down. Do not leave any box blank. Type ‘no’ or ‘n/a’ if you don’t have a response.
Briefly describe what you were asked to do in this experiment? (if there is existing text in the box delete it.
debrief.response: try to end up with the most amount of points by figuring out the pattern of what will give you the most points

debrief.itemText: Was there any part of the experiment that you found to be confusing?

debrief.response: which sequence of patterns would give me the most points. it also feels like the time given for the numbers and letter trials were shorter on some patterns. and some gave a lot of points for just sticking with the letters for the entire duration of a trial
